company_name: WKH WERKZEUG- KUNSTSTOFF - LD HDPE UND FOLIENHANDEL GMBH
information: The company WKH WERKZEUG- KUNSTSTOFF - LD HDPE UND FOLIENHANDEL GMBH, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, which operates in the ORGANIC FARMING industry. It also operates in the Pets industries. It is based in Emlichheim, Germany.
